.TH LOOTSHEET-INIT 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-init \\- Initialize a fresh LootSheet database
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet init [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet init

Bootstraps a fresh SQLite database from the embedded schema and seed accounts.
If the configured database already contains LootSheet metadata, init reports that it is already initialized and does not reseed it.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for init
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet(1)
